<inglise> At the time of signing of the contract or agreement, the contractor shall lodge a security equal to at least 4 % of the value of the contract or the agreement to guarantee its performance. </inglise>
<eesti> Lepingu v&otilde;i kokkuleppe allkirjastamise ajal esitab lepinguosaline oma tegevuse tagamiseks tagatise, mis on v&otilde;rdne v&auml;hemalt nelja protsendiga lepingu v&otilde;i kokkuleppe v&auml;&auml;rtusest. </eesti>
